cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

This paper focuses on video prediction using adversarial generative models, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also proposes a novel recurrent unit for the generator, which involves learning motion-like features and handling complex behavior, indicating a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper deals with large-scale datasets, which suggests a potential fit for multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
